reviewText: The video compliments the book. Great way to evangelize!
This DVD is wonderful. Scientific proof of Christ in the Eucharist .

If you are Catholic you should see this, if not you need to see this and enforce or reinforce your faith.  As in the past, still in the present.  There are two follow up dvd's to this that cover the same information but in better detail.
Testing of hosts that have been transformed into heart muscle!  Facinating and faith building!
